<h1>GET STEAM NOW</h1>
<h2>IN MINUTES, <em>YOU'LL BE PLAYING YOUR FAVORITE GAMES</em></h2>
<img src="images/Graphic_box.jpg" width="24" height="6" alt=""><br>
<div class="narrower">
<br>We've split the Steam installers into seperate versions based on the game cache they include.  Links marked with (BT) require that you have <a href="http://www.filerush.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=10" target="_blank">Bit Torrent</a> installed.<br>
<br>
{% for category in categories %}
<h3>{{ category.name }}{% if category.file_size %}: ({{ category.file_size }}){% endif %}</h3><br>
<table width="525" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    {% set categoryLinks = links|filter(l => l.category == category.name) %}
    {% for row in categoryLinks|batch(3, '') %}
    <tr>
        {% for link in row %}
        <td width="33%">
            {% if link %}
            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                    <td nowrap><img src="images/black_button2_leftside.gif" width="10" height="20"></td>
                    <td bgcolor="#000000" nowrap width="150"><a class="maize" href="{{ link.url }}" style="font-size: 11px;">{{ link.label }}</a></td>
                    <td nowrap><img src="images/black_button2_rightside.gif" width="10" height="20"></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            {% endif %}
        </td>
        {% endfor %}
    </tr>
    <tr><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><br></td></tr>
    {% endfor %}
</table>
<br>
{% endfor %}
<hr>
{{ system_requirements|raw }}
</div>
